{"tid":141835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港申辦同志運動會　成首個入圍亞洲城市","createTime":"2017-03-03T08:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T18:59:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a63c38d3c6b69373fffc97367ff27a00d0a0ed08","tid":141835,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170303/s00001/1488523343594_8AA9F2258D57CD247D8DB656C020F444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170303%2Fs00001%2F1488523343594_8AA9F2258D57CD247D8DB656C020F444.jpg&h=872100ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港申辦同志運動會組織主席戚本乙（左）、Dennis Philipse（右）。（李詠珊攝)<br />\n<br />\n香港成為首個入圍申辦同志運動會的亞洲城市，晉身2022年第十一屆同志運動會申辦城市的候選名單，將與華盛頓特區和墨西哥瓜達拉哈拉角逐主辦城市。 <br />\n<br />\n同志運動會早於1982年開始於三藩市首次舉辦，而下屆同志運動會將於2018年在巴黎舉行，過去未曾於亞洲城市舉行，若香港成功成為申辦城市，將會是首個亞洲城市舉辦該運動會。<br />\n<br />\n組織主席Dennis Philipse解釋，同志運動會除了有36種不同的運動競技項目，亦包含藝術和文化交流會，他指現時需籌募1.5萬美元（港幣約11.6萬元）作申辦費用，而預計整個運動會需投放650萬美元（港幣約5045萬元），但同時可於運動會期間吸引1.5萬名來自各地的參加者和約4萬名遊客，可為香港的旅遊業帶來收益。<br />\n<br />\n組織另一名主席戚本乙指，籌辦過程中，因為公眾對同志運動會的認識不多，因此難於宣傳，她又指，由於運動會的英文名字為「Gay Games」，令很多人都誤以為該運動會只舉辦予同性戀者，她強調，該運動會不分族群、年齡和性取向人士，均可參與，亦藉此宣揚共融訊息，她期望之後可把握機會向公眾解釋。<br />\n<br />\n同志運動委員會將於5月到香港作現場考察，申辦組織亦需遠赴巴黎簡介有關計劃，而11月就會公布有關結果。<br />\n<br />\n戚本乙認為，香港有一定的優勢，因為該運動會未曾於亞洲城市舉辦，而香港本是個能包容多元文化的城市，很適合作為於亞洲舉辦同志運動會的起點，而香港亦有不同的運動設施和場館滿足各運動的需要，她有一定信心爭取為申辦城市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170303/s00001/1488523512355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170303%2Fs00001%2F1488523512355&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=0b6eff32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170303%2Fs00001%2F1488523512355&h=a7c529db\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170303/s00001/1488523512355</a>"},{"pid":"318378659594d2bafd0a557d48e86a6252a4bff0","tid":141835,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"有咩意義"},{"pid":"7b4308270b8325b9bafa441a3b73a43b2b399c75","tid":141835,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:59:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"081faf24a831eb3353734a794b1e9d4f61cc130c","tid":141835,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:02:46.000Z","msg":"明光社係時候發功啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341b9c487efcc0c84efab10a1011a0c4d44cd38b","tid":141835,"uid":29317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:03:31.000Z","msg":"咩運動?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60c4b0e4c92095f0f164d8fa86a742ffcf2ee94","tid":141835,"uid":85498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班大隻1比劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n格劍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed12eca3b9e44ceb1e4ca219fed5a66223814df","tid":141835,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:08:52.000Z","msg":"多人劍擊比賽"},{"pid":"edb84e77bc1999c942559af35a8ff72ed926bae5","tid":141835,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"保護後欄大賽弓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0838ea25d304799199f34e8b2cc737258c36b53b","tid":141835,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"<